
== Kinect project repos

Directories description
    glmf: GLMF tutorial and first shot on kinect hacking
    viewer: Simplified version of programs mentionned above, just display depth data with opencv
    HandTracking: Perform a complete mouse control through Nite (no cmake support yet)
    HandSegment: Intend to improve hand gesture recognition (not yet built)

Note: Built process depends on OpenNi and Nite libraries location, be sure to adapt makefiles or CMakeLists.txt 

